<html><head>
$wims_html_header
</head><body $wims_htmlbody>
!headmenu

!!if $cmd=help
 !!read help.phtml
 !!goto end
!!endif

<center><h1>WIMS at $httpd_HTTP_HOST
<p>
Creation of a message board
</h1></center> <p><hr width="50%"> <p>

!if $toomany=yes
 !read toomany.phtml
 !goto end
!endif

!read names.phtml
!if $error!=$empty
 <p>
 !read msg.phtml
 <p>
 !href module=$module&cmd=reply&step=0 Restart the operation.
 <p>
 !goto end
!endif

!if $step=$empty or $step=0
 !set password=
 !set passsup=
 If you create a message board on this WIMS site,
 you should assume the responsibility of its maintenance. <p>
 To create your message board, please fill in the following informations.
 !form reply
 <input type=hidden name=step value=1>
 <ul>
 <li>Name of the message board (at most $titlelim characters):
  <input size=$titlelim name=title value="$title"> <p>
 <li>Description (at most $desclim characters):
  <textarea cols=65 rows=5 name=description>$description</textarea> <p>
 <li>Complete name of its owner (that is, you):
  <input size=$suplim name=supervisor value="$supervisor"> <p>
 <li>Email address:
  <input size=$emaillim name=email value="$email"> <br>
  (Your message board won't be created unless you give
  your email address which works right now.)<p>
 <li>Choose a owner's password:
  <input size=16 type=password name=passsup> <br>
  (between 4 and 16 characters, digits or letters without accent). <br>
  This password will allow you to access the message board as its owner.
  You should be the only person to know it. <p>
 <li>Choose a password of the message board:
  <input size=16 type=password name=password> <br>
  (between 4 and 16 characters, digits or letters without accent). <br>
  This password will be required for the register of users of the message
  board; you can therefore diffuse it to anybody whom you allow to participate
  in the discussions. <p>
 </ul>
 <center><input type=submit value="Continue"></center>
 </form>

 !goto end
!endif

!if $step=1
 Hello, $supervisor!<p>
 You are creating a message board $forumname on the WIMS site
 $httpd_HTTP_HOST.
 <p>
 If you find an error in the above informations, please
 !href module=$module&cmd=reply&step=0 correct it.
 <p>Otherwise, in order to verify the exactness of your passwords,
 please type them again. <p>
 !form reply
 <input type=hidden name=step value=2>
 Owner's password:
 <input type=password name=passsup> <p>
 !if $pword!=$empty
  Password of the message board:
  <input type=password name=password> <p>
 !endif
 <center><input type=submit value="Continue"></center>
 </form>
 !goto end1
!endif

!if $step=2
 Hello, $supervisor!<p>
 Now you need a code to finish the operation of creation of a new message
 board under WIMS at the site $http_HTTP_HOST. <p>
 This code has just been sent to your email address
 ``<tt>$email</tt>''. Please go to verify your email box (wait a little bit
 if necessary), and read this message.
 Pick up the code in the message, and copy it below.
 !form reply
 <input type=hidden name=step value=3>
 <center>Code of the message board: <input size=16 name=typecode>
 <p><input type=submit value="Continue"></center>
 </form>
 <b>Attention</b> This code is only used once here. It cannot be used to
 connect to the message board!
 <p>
 !goto end1
!endif

!if $step=3
 Hello, $supervisor!<p>
 Your message board $forumname is now created. Congratulations, and enjoy!<p>
 You can access your message board
 !href module=adm/forum/forum from here
.
 !goto end
!endif

:end1
<p>
!href module=$module&cmd=reply&step=0 Back to the beginning of the operation.
:end
!tail

!set step=

